{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/household-and-housing/domestic-violence-prevention","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Domestic violence prevention","meta_description":"Threatened by your partner or another household member due to violence or coercion.","content":{"processed":"<h2><strong>Recommendations</strong></h2>\n<p>If you feel <strong>threatened</strong> by your partner or another household member due to mental, physical or sexual violence or coercion, immediately <strong>contact the helpline for domestic violence.</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Crime and Domestic Violence Helpline <em>White Circle of Safety</em>: <strong>116 006</strong> (non-stop), FREE help for victims.</li>\n<li>Helpline for victims of domestic and sexual violence <em>proFem</em> <strong>+420 608 222 277</strong>, social worker - Monday to Friday 9:00 - 15:00, the legal helpline for victims of domestic and sexual violence - Tuesday 9:00 - 12:00 and Wednesday 17:30 - 20:30.</li>\n</ul><p>In case of a <strong>direct threat</strong>, please <strong>contact Police of the Czech Republic on line 158.</strong></p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/household-and-housing/domestic-violence-prevention"},"valid_from":null,"links":[{"uri":"https://www.domacinasili.cz/domaci-nasili/","title":"White Circle of Safety: Information on domestic violence"},{"uri":"https://www.profem.cz/cs","title":"The proFem movement "},{"uri":"http://www.uracr.cz/koroporadna","title":"Union of Family Lawyers"}],"relationships":{"region":[],"icon":null,"situation_type":{"name":"Household and housing","path":{"alias":"/situations/household-and-housing"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"home"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Helplines","path":{"alias":"/situations/stress-and-handling-impacts-pandemic/helplines","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Alcohol and substance use","path":{"alias":"/situations/stress-and-handling-impacts-pandemic/alcohol-and-substance-use